      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine with no signs of wear on the leather or carpets. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been garage-kept and meticulously serviced; it drives exactly like a brand-new car. Every feature and electronic component functions flawlessly, making this a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a showroom-quality vehicle.",
