    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, ensuring a dependable and enjoyable ride for its next owner. It's a solid, reliable choice that's ready for many more miles on the road. You'll love the smooth handling and the care that has clearly been put into keeping it in great shape!",
